    "description": "时长不长却拥有超棒的视觉体验，将其艺术理念以新技术进行完美体现。—— 来自 细拉<br>CowLevel: 5/5<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/2e5681eac2e39b4153da71e04f1b4f32.poster.avif?t=1763154932\" width=628 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/2e5681eac2e39b4153da71e04f1b4f32.webm?t=1763154932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/2e5681eac2e39b4153da71e04f1b4f32.mp4?t=1763154932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>有史以来最为广受好评的游戏之一终于在PC平台闪亮登场：你将能获得全方位令人炫目的游戏体验，狂轰滥炸地打败一波波敌人以及巨大的变形头目，伴随着的是和Rez的传奇电子音乐同步交融的声与色。<br><br>不管你是选择在标准桌面模式游玩还是在VR中完全沉浸式的游玩，《Rez Infinite》的真正魅力必然需要你亲眼——以及亲耳——才能体会。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/b4f2a817f880e1086b911a94c4bb6130.poster.avif?t=1763154932\" width=628 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/b4f2a817f880e1086b911a94c4bb6130.webm?t=1763154932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/b4f2a817f880e1086b911a94c4bb6130.mp4?t=1763154932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >关键要素</h2></strong><br><strong>终极合集</strong><br>完全重制的经典Rez关卡，从Areas 1到5应有尽有，并且还包括在Area X全新的自由飞翔体验。<br><br><strong>最高清的Rez</strong><br>无限制的分辨率，最高能两倍于过去任何版本Rez的材质分辨率，这些要素都能让游戏展现出剃刀般锋利的视觉效果。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/685fa39ce39a6330ca258ef31cf386b2.poster.avif?t=1763154932\" width=628 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/685fa39ce39a6330ca258ef31cf386b2.webm?t=1763154932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/685fa39ce39a6330ca258ef31cf386b2.mp4?t=1763154932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>增强的音响效果</strong><br>完整的3D音效成就了Rez的出色音乐以及音效。<br><br><strong>VR选项</strong><br>整个游戏都能在桌面系统下游玩，也可以使用HTC VIVE或者Oculus Rift头戴及附属控制器（支持标准游戏手柄、Vive操控手柄、Oculus Remote以及Touch控制器）在完整VR模式下游玩。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/3408e60f0eaca3940494b2991b738e65.poster.avif?t=1763154932\" width=628 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/3408e60f0eaca3940494b2991b738e65.webm?t=1763154932\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/636450/extras/3408e60f0eaca3940494b2991b738e65.mp4?t=1763154932\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
